,"text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuruwHapN","text_ar":"صُرُوحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, Msb,) [both strangely said in the K, to be substs.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, pure, sheer, free from admixture, unmingled, unmixed, genuine,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clear;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K;) said of a thing (S, O, Msb) of any kind of which the meaning is predicable, (S, O,) [and particularly] said of one's race, or genealogy. (K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaraHa","text_ar":"صَرَحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 2, in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n24137","headword_ar":"صَرْحٌ","root":"SrH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSor","text_ar":"قَصْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pavilion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (Zj, S, A, K:) and (as some say, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any lofty building:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chamber, built apart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"detached, large, and lofty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuruwHN","text_ar":"صُرُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, A.)"}],"source_refs":["Zj","S","A","K","TA","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n24138","headword_ar":"صَرَحٌ","root":"SrH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SariyH","text_ar":"صَرِيح"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}